WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.025 --> 00:00:14.384
''If my people, who are called by
my name, will humble themselves

00:00:14.584 --> 00:00:18.002
and pray and seek my face
and turn from their wicked ways,

00:00:18.202 --> 00:00:21.634
then I will hear from heaven,
and I will forgive their sin

00:00:21.834 --> 00:00:28.568
and will heal their land.''
(2 Chronicles 7:14)

00:00:41.114 --> 00:00:43.186
Let’s go there, O.K.?

00:00:44.527 --> 00:00:46.837
MATERNITY HOSPITAL

00:00:48.589 --> 00:00:50.311
What? What?

00:00:53.193 --> 00:00:57.260
Because of the pregnancy,
all my emotions were mixed.

00:00:57.460 --> 00:01:03.470
Happiness, sadness.
I can't explain it. Fear.

00:01:03.670 --> 00:01:07.410
Knowing that I wouldn't be able
to work if I felt unwell,

00:01:07.610 --> 00:01:10.980
that I wouldn't be able to take care
of my 2-year-old child,

00:01:11.180 --> 00:01:14.980
that I wouldn't be able to take her
to kindergarden if I felt unwell.

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:17.450
No one can do this
if my husband is at work.

00:01:18.180 --> 00:01:20.980
Knowing that I couldn't
work and contribute,

00:01:21.180 --> 00:01:24.910
and that one paycheck
covered only utilities and rent.

00:01:25.110 --> 00:01:30.570
I hastily decided that I would
abort my baby, that I could do it.

00:01:30.770 --> 00:01:33.400
I lived for two weeks
certain that I could do it.

00:01:33.600 --> 00:01:39.640
What's horrible is that,
suddenly, I had no emotions.

00:01:39.840 --> 00:01:44.940
My emotions turned from happiness
to the belief I would abort the baby.

00:01:45.170 --> 00:01:47.370
As if it were that simple.

00:01:47.570 --> 00:01:54.422
I went for a check-up at the Merkur
Hospital and arranged everything.

00:01:54.622 --> 00:01:56.542
When I arrived on the arranged day,

00:01:56.742 --> 00:02:00.212
my husband couldn't go with me
because there were no parking spaces.

00:02:00.412 --> 00:02:04.182
He left everything to me
because he couldn't do it.

00:02:04.382 --> 00:02:05.892
He simply couldn't do it.

00:02:06.092 --> 00:02:08.016
At the beginning, it was difficult.

00:02:08.216 --> 00:02:11.178
I left her and I went away,
because it was difficult.

00:02:11.378 --> 00:02:14.086
I didn't tell her that.
I didn't tell her many things.

00:02:14.286 --> 00:02:18.070
I fell into the hands of a nurse
who started telling me,

00:02:18.773 --> 00:02:22.312
''Are you sure? Don't do it.
You'll kill your child.

00:02:22.512 --> 00:02:24.546
As if you killed the one you have.''

00:02:24.746 --> 00:02:29.435
As if I didn't already know this.
But I felt I had to do it.

00:02:29.635 --> 00:02:35.622
She sent me to a woman at the stand.
''I want to live!'' -unborn child

00:02:35.822 --> 00:02:38.612
She was very cheerful and lively.

00:02:38.812 --> 00:02:44.322
She told me not to do this and
gave me a number to call for help.

00:02:44.522 --> 00:02:48.272
I told her to leave me alone and
that no one in the world could help me.

00:02:48.472 --> 00:02:51.852
She said: ''Yes they can!
Just call the number.''

00:02:52.052 --> 00:02:54.302
I didn't want to,
so I ran away from her.

00:02:54.502 --> 00:03:00.370
I sat by the road and cried frantically
because I didn't know what to do.

00:03:00.570 --> 00:03:02.732
Of course I'm happy.

00:03:03.232 --> 00:03:07.552
Especially because now I have a son,
and Gabrijela will have a brother.

00:03:10.652 --> 00:03:14.536
I would have been very sorry
if she had had an abortion. Very sorry.

00:03:14.736 --> 00:03:17.432
But you came and helped us.

00:03:17.632 --> 00:03:19.692
Here they come.

00:03:22.242 --> 00:03:26.042
That's my brother.
We mustn't touch little brother.

00:03:28.818 --> 00:03:32.378
Who is that? –Little brother!
-Whose brother? -Mine!

00:03:32.878 --> 00:03:35.844
Whose little brother?
–That's my little brother!

00:03:42.272 --> 00:03:52.660
40 DAYS...

00:03:53.660 --> 00:03:58.247
Humanity today is facing
one of the greatest crises in history.

00:03:58.447 --> 00:04:01.927
This crisis is literally
destroying human lives.

00:04:02.127 --> 00:04:07.247
It is hurting women especially,
but also tearing families apart.

00:04:07.447 --> 00:04:10.267
This crisis has caused big problems,

00:04:10.467 --> 00:04:14.697
not only on a local level,
but also on a global scale.

00:04:14.897 --> 00:04:16.887
And that is abortion.

00:04:17.087 --> 00:04:20.467
On an annual basis,
only through a clinical procedure,

00:04:21.137 --> 00:04:25.447
more than 56 million
children are aborted.

00:04:26.147 --> 00:04:31.007
The number of aborted children
on an annual basis is bigger than

00:04:31.207 --> 00:04:35.087
all the other human casulties together.

00:04:35.287 --> 00:04:40.509
I WANT TO BE WITH YOU, MOM
-I did something like that.

00:04:41.077 --> 00:04:45.697
And, believe me, I know the name
of the child, the sex of the child.

00:04:46.787 --> 00:04:51.779
And every time I see
a child of the same sex,

00:04:51.979 --> 00:04:55.302
I ask myself a hundred times
what colour its eyes would have been.

00:04:56.617 --> 00:04:59.365
What kind of little girl she would be.

00:05:00.467 --> 00:05:06.232
This is a wound you can't erase.
And even though I forgave myself,

00:05:06.432 --> 00:05:09.760
and people around me,
and the Lord forgave me,

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:13.834
this can't be erased.
It is really hard.

00:05:14.034 --> 00:05:16.640
When you don't think about it,
the life just goes on,

00:05:16.840 --> 00:05:20.398
but when you go into the depths of it,
you can't escape from it.

00:05:20.598 --> 00:05:25.704
The reason I considered abortion
was the pressure from my family.

00:05:25.904 --> 00:05:30.261
''What do you need one more child for?
You're young. You have time for kids.

00:05:30.761 --> 00:05:32.988
You're digging yourself
into a hole.''

00:05:33.388 --> 00:05:39.679
All these words created
a confusion in my head.

00:05:40.279 --> 00:05:46.631
I went to hospital for a check-up
and to arrange to have an abortion.

00:05:46.831 --> 00:05:52.519
The doctor told me to take
a look at the monitor,

00:05:52.719 --> 00:05:55.266
because I didn't have the
strength to look at it.

00:05:56.464 --> 00:06:02.755
Then I saw those little hands
and feet, its heart beating,

00:06:02.955 --> 00:06:07.157
and then it came to me that
Danijel was just the same.

00:06:07.357 --> 00:06:10.720
That he is now a real child.

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:16.093
I just couldn't do it.

00:06:18.563 --> 00:06:21.205
A person then asks oneself
what can one do about it.

00:06:21.405 --> 00:06:24.870
How can I as an individual
make a change in this world

00:06:25.070 --> 00:06:28.489
which has strayed
into a huge emptiness?

00:06:28.689 --> 00:06:31.859
What can I as a human being
do to help my neighbour?

00:06:34.485 --> 00:06:38.069
Most Holy Soul of Christ,
Masterpiece of the Holy Trinity.

00:06:38.269 --> 00:06:39.858
Sanctify us.

00:06:40.058 --> 00:06:43.831
Most Holy Soul of Christ, Archetype
of the perfection of creation.

00:06:44.031 --> 00:06:45.508
Sanctify us.

00:06:45.708 --> 00:06:48.958
Most Holy Soul of Christ,
King of eternal glory.

00:06:49.158 --> 00:06:50.618
Sanctify us.

00:06:50.818 --> 00:06:55.860
Most Holy Soul of Christ, Ark of all
the graces and gifts of the Holy Spirit.

00:06:56.060 --> 00:06:57.428
Sanctify us.

00:06:57.628 --> 00:07:02.641
Most Holy Soul of Christ, Founder of
the Church bearing hosts of saints.

00:07:02.841 --> 00:07:04.584
Sanctify us.

00:07:05.564 --> 00:07:11.080
40 Days for Life is the biggest
pro-life initiative in the world.

00:07:11.280 --> 00:07:13.616
It's an ecumenical
and Christian initiative

00:07:13.816 --> 00:07:17.100
gathering all Christians
in the fight for life.

00:07:17.300 --> 00:07:20.859
It gathers more than 750,000
people around the world,

00:07:21.059 --> 00:07:22.977
and consists of 3 key elements:

00:07:23.177 --> 00:07:27.682
prayer and fasting, peaceful vigil,
and community outreach.

00:07:27.882 --> 00:07:30.628
Without prayer and fasting
we can't do anything.

00:07:30.828 --> 00:07:34.226
Prayer and fasting are the foundation
on which we can build

00:07:34.426 --> 00:07:39.031
everything we plan to do for our Lord,

00:07:39.231 --> 00:07:42.359
and everything we want to allow
the Lord to do through us.

00:07:42.559 --> 00:07:47.840
This is a method. The way of
God's Kingdom. The way of Heaven.

00:07:48.040 --> 00:07:52.819
We people have our own methods and
thoughts, but the Lord has taught us

00:07:53.019 --> 00:07:55.785
that only through prayer and fasting,

00:07:55.985 --> 00:08:02.380
through humility,
through a silent or loud presence,

00:08:02.580 --> 00:08:08.857
we can give glory to God and save those
for whom Christ spilled His blood.

00:08:10.219 --> 00:08:15.618
Deliver us, Jesus!
Deliver us, Jesus!

00:08:17.247 --> 00:08:22.361
If I had known about it before,
believe me, I wouldn't have done it.

00:08:22.561 --> 00:08:29.315
I only became aware of it
when I started a spiritual retreat.

00:08:29.515 --> 00:08:32.412
It didn't concern me much.

00:08:32.612 --> 00:08:37.812
It was something that had passed.
No one had even taught us about it.

00:08:38.012 --> 00:08:40.642
Well, it posed a problem
for our careers.

00:08:40.842 --> 00:08:44.128
We thought that we would have
more babies, that there was time.

00:08:44.328 --> 00:08:48.014
We did not think about it
as a child that is unique.

00:08:48.214 --> 00:08:53.291
It was something that happened, that
could be solved by a medical procedure.

00:08:53.491 --> 00:08:56.675
Of course, it wasn't like that.
The procedure was done,

00:08:56.875 --> 00:09:03.039
but it opened many wounds in our
hearts and led to distrust between us.

00:09:03.239 --> 00:09:06.191
Because I did not protect her,
as a real man should do.

00:09:06.391 --> 00:09:09.426
I also lost my trust in women.

00:09:09.626 --> 00:09:14.384
That what we were created to be,
to have a child and start a family,

00:09:14.584 --> 00:09:18.510
we destroyed everything in
a moment of not thinking.

00:09:18.710 --> 00:09:22.328
People say that one loves
the unwanted child in a special way.

00:09:22.528 --> 00:09:28.738
And that is true. But I can't say
that I love Danijel or her more.

00:09:28.938 --> 00:09:31.931
I love them the same.
But she is special.

00:09:32.131 --> 00:09:35.674
My Antonia will turn two soon.

00:09:36.530 --> 00:09:41.429
I can say that during
these two years of her life,

00:09:42.029 --> 00:09:44.992
I have learned a lot.

00:09:46.487 --> 00:09:49.049
My life has changed.

00:09:49.249 --> 00:09:56.641
My motherly love has grown deeper
because I was at the end of my ropes.

00:09:57.960 --> 00:10:04.493
Should I terminate the pregnancy
or give birth to that precious life.

00:10:04.693 --> 00:10:06.578
We pray and fast throughout the year

00:10:06.778 --> 00:10:09.691
for the end of abortion
in Croatia and the world.

00:10:09.891 --> 00:10:13.548
Twice a year, in front of hospitals
and health centres across Croatia

00:10:13.748 --> 00:10:15.985
and around the whole world,
at the same time,

00:10:16.185 --> 00:10:21.715
we stand in vigil for 40 days, as
the last sign of hope, mercy and love

00:10:21.915 --> 00:10:24.866
for those mothers and families
considering abortion,

00:10:25.066 --> 00:10:30.236
and as the first sign of mercy for
those afflicted by the wound of abortion

00:10:30.436 --> 00:10:36.134
and who want to find consolation,
forgiveness, and repent for that sin.

00:10:36.334 --> 00:10:40.574
I would never have done what I did
if I had had the understanding of it,

00:10:40.774 --> 00:10:44.691
as the mothers today have.
There is hope for them.

00:10:44.891 --> 00:10:47.912
I have never been sorry
for giving birth to my two children,

00:10:48.112 --> 00:10:52.458
but I have never found consolation
for having lost many of my children,

00:10:52.658 --> 00:10:54.668
in this way or the other.

00:10:54.868 --> 00:11:00.206
My mom wasn't happy because
she is on social support herself

00:11:00.406 --> 00:11:02.656
and she didn't know
how we would manage.

00:11:03.925 --> 00:11:07.912
She told me not to come home
because we have nothing to life off.

00:11:08.112 --> 00:11:13.553
My boyfriend said he didn't care
and that I could do whatever I wanted.

00:11:13.753 --> 00:11:18.612
And that he couldn't promise to be
with me. That it was my decision.

00:11:18.812 --> 00:11:24.957
My aunt went to talk to a woman
praying in front of the hospital.

00:11:25.157 --> 00:11:31.595
I went to hospital on appointment
and saw people praying outside.

00:11:31.795 --> 00:11:36.996
At first, I didn't understand why they
were praying, but I noticed a number.

00:11:37.196 --> 00:11:42.792
And above that number
there was written 40 Days for Life.

00:11:42.992 --> 00:11:48.424
I approached the girl standing behind
the sign and asked about the number.

00:11:48.624 --> 00:11:51.253
She said they were a pro-life
association called ''Betlehem'',

00:11:51.453 --> 00:11:53.746
and they were fighting
for life for 40 days.

00:11:53.946 --> 00:12:00.218
I told her my story. I cried.
It was very difficult for me.

00:12:01.964 --> 00:12:05.042
She invited me to move
to the side and so we did.

00:12:07.013 --> 00:12:11.173
She told me very caringly and lovingly
that there was no reason to be afraid

00:12:11.373 --> 00:12:14.413
because we had the support of
both the Association ''Betlehem''

00:12:14.613 --> 00:12:19.833
and 40 Days for Life.
She told me to contact them freely,

00:12:20.033 --> 00:12:22.801
and that they were there for us
for everything we needed.

00:12:23.001 --> 00:12:25.594
That we should be calm
and everything would be fine.

00:12:25.794 --> 00:12:30.268
I needed attention and care.
I needed support.

00:12:31.707 --> 00:12:36.997
I thought I was alone. I needed
someone who would understand me

00:12:37.197 --> 00:12:41.935
and who would support my
decision for the life of my child.

00:12:42.135 --> 00:12:46.921
Of my little girl whom I have been
carrying for nine months.

00:12:47.121 --> 00:12:50.855
I am happy and grateful
to them for everything.

00:12:51.055 --> 00:12:56.587
As well as to my aunt
who let me stay at her place

00:12:56.787 --> 00:13:00.467
and who is always with me and
who is present at my every check-up.

00:13:00.667 --> 00:13:04.259
I believe that every mother carrying
a baby underneath her heart

00:13:04.459 --> 00:13:05.853
feels love towards it.

00:13:06.053 --> 00:13:08.157
She only needs a little
courage and encouragement.

00:13:08.357 --> 00:13:10.864
That we are here for them
and that somebody cares.

00:13:11.064 --> 00:13:14.269
We do care. In conversation,
without even counseling,

00:13:14.469 --> 00:13:17.685
just to listen to them
and see what troubles their heart,

00:13:17.885 --> 00:13:21.536
we have felt that already
this brings great fruit.

00:13:28.162 --> 00:13:31.317
Should I put her here?
–The other way around.

00:13:31.517 --> 00:13:32.763
Or here perhaps?

00:13:38.848 --> 00:13:42.696
That's Russia! –No, ha?
-Don't send me to France!

00:13:42.896 --> 00:13:44.444
Why? Are you afraid of dying?

00:13:44.644 --> 00:13:48.316
I'm not afraid of dying.
It's just because.

00:13:48.516 --> 00:13:50.512
''Now choose life!''

00:14:06.862 --> 00:14:09.819
''No one can do it for me,

00:14:10.419 --> 00:14:15.413
to carry my cross,
to fulfil Your plan.

00:14:15.613 --> 00:14:18.460
No one can do it for me,

00:14:18.960 --> 00:14:23.619
to overcome my fears,
to endure my battles.

00:14:23.819 --> 00:14:27.100
Because You call me by my name.

00:14:27.300 --> 00:14:32.354
I am neither letter nor number, but
engraved in the palm of Your hand.

00:14:32.554 --> 00:14:35.685
HUMAN RIGHTS BEGIN WITH CONCEPTION
''You call me by my name.

00:14:35.885 --> 00:14:41.789
I am neither letter nor number,
but the one You died for.

00:14:41.989 --> 00:14:44.231
EVERY LIFE IS GOD’S GIFT
PRAY TO END ABORTION

00:14:44.431 --> 00:14:47.336
This is my life, my battle and pain,

00:14:47.536 --> 00:14:52.218
my joy and salvation,
my cross and blessing.

00:14:52.418 --> 00:14:55.816
This is my life, my battle and pain,

00:14:56.016 --> 00:15:03.122
my joy and salvation, both
a cross and blessing from Heaven."

00:15:03.322 --> 00:15:07.026
I'm a child conceived by rape in 1992.

00:15:07.226 --> 00:15:09.675
My mother brought me to this world.

00:15:09.875 --> 00:15:14.400
She brought me to this world
with great love, of course.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:19.176
The only support she had
was our dear God.

00:15:19.376 --> 00:15:21.912
She surrendered everything
to Him and told Him that

00:15:22.112 --> 00:15:26.619
she would carry this pregnancy
to the end, despite the difficulties,

00:15:26.819 --> 00:15:32.904
despite persuasions both from
the doctor and the whole family.

00:15:33.104 --> 00:15:39.251
I can only be grateful to her that
I'm alive and that she gave me life.

00:15:39.451 --> 00:15:44.219
I can only return her
the love she gave me

00:15:44.419 --> 00:15:48.855
and be thankful to her
every day for giving me life.

00:15:49.055 --> 00:15:52.214
Many children in this world
aren't born.

00:15:52.414 --> 00:15:56.419
When I started praying in front
of the hospital and becoming aware

00:15:56.619 --> 00:16:01.037
of the moment of conception,
that life is a gift, and the unborn...

00:16:01.237 --> 00:16:08.464
Everything stirred inside me, and my
heart and my life got a new meaning.

00:16:08.664 --> 00:16:12.712
I started reaching deeper into myself

00:16:12.912 --> 00:16:15.917
and my own existence,
and the reason why I'm here.

00:16:16.117 --> 00:16:22.406
Of course, the wound is big.
The sorrow and sadness are great,

00:16:22.606 --> 00:16:27.884
when one realises that something as
beautiful as the beginning of a new life

00:16:28.084 --> 00:16:31.737
actually occurred in a trauma.
But something good came out of it.

00:16:31.937 --> 00:16:36.598
I was born. And I'm thankful to God
and my mother that I was born.

00:16:36.798 --> 00:16:43.674
I'm praying here because I had
a close encounter with abortion

00:16:43.874 --> 00:16:48.314
through the case of my late wife,
and her fight with breast cancer.

00:16:48.514 --> 00:16:53.719
At one point, her illness progressed,
and the doctor notified me that

00:16:53.919 --> 00:16:57.021
there would come the moment when
a decision would have to be made:

00:16:57.221 --> 00:16:58.980
either the baby or my wife.

00:16:59.180 --> 00:17:02.141
I didn't think about the possibility
of abortion at all.

00:17:02.341 --> 00:17:06.353
I only thought about being with
my wife, in any way possible.

00:17:06.553 --> 00:17:10.598
Eventually, my daughter was born.
Healthy, thank God.

00:17:10.798 --> 00:17:14.436
I have to emphasise
that after that decision,

00:17:14.636 --> 00:17:17.938
when you finally come to it,
God becomes very merciful.

00:17:18.138 --> 00:17:20.620
God gives his grace abundantly
and He helped me immensely,

00:17:20.820 --> 00:17:26.381
because my wife gave birth without any
problems or complications whatsoever.

00:17:26.581 --> 00:17:33.429
My child wasn't sick, even though
my wife had galloping breast cancer.

00:17:33.629 --> 00:17:35.429
God protected her from everything.

00:17:35.629 --> 00:17:41.405
The case with my wife instilled in me
the love for the prayer for the unborn,

00:17:41.605 --> 00:17:44.011
which I am doing now
in front of the hospital.

00:17:49.489 --> 00:17:53.587
I want us to have a walk in the city.
We have one common place.

00:17:57.460 --> 00:18:02.114
When I found out about the pregnancy,
I was quite shocked and confused.

00:18:02.314 --> 00:18:07.053
It was a great amount
of negative emotions.

00:18:08.751 --> 00:18:13.598
Disapproval and deprecation of people
around me also contributed to it.

00:18:14.922 --> 00:18:18.396
They literally pushed me
to have an abortion.

00:18:18.596 --> 00:18:23.804
But in my heart I didn't feel
that was the right thing to do.

00:18:24.004 --> 00:18:26.077
I felt the right thing
was to give birth.

00:18:26.277 --> 00:18:30.371
Little by little, things got better.

00:18:30.571 --> 00:18:36.069
And today I have a 6-month-old baby.

00:18:36.269 --> 00:18:38.537
I'm very happy.

00:18:38.737 --> 00:18:43.713
And I know that I made
the only right choice.

00:19:00.641 --> 00:19:02.920
I am already tired of Rome!

00:19:34.895 --> 00:19:37.439
International conference
''Save more lives'', London, 2017

00:22:49.725 --> 00:22:50.725
There he is!

00:23:16.899 --> 00:23:20.232
I have presented to the Pope
our pro-life movement in Croatia.

00:23:20.432 --> 00:23:26.003
I introduced to him our proud mother
Dalia and her daughter, our Nika.

00:23:26.203 --> 00:23:29.923
All of us together. I asked him for
his blessing and his short message.

00:23:30.123 --> 00:23:32.653
The Pope said:
"Just continue going forward.

00:23:32.853 --> 00:23:37.753
Do as much as you can to save
as many babies as possible.

00:23:37.953 --> 00:23:41.283
I'm with you. Pray for me.
I'll be praying for you!"

00:23:41.483 --> 00:23:45.283
He gave us his blessing and we are
very happy and excited because of it.

00:23:45.483 --> 00:23:49.425
We gave the Holy Father the painting
of the Most Holy Soul of Jesus Christ.

00:23:49.625 --> 00:23:52.654
This is a wonderful devotion
connected with

00:23:52.854 --> 00:23:55.655
the dignity and sanctity of human life.

00:23:55.855 --> 00:23:58.036
I briefly explained to him
what it is about.

00:23:58.236 --> 00:24:02.964
It is a devotion from Poland, from
the time of St Faustina Kowalska.

00:24:03.164 --> 00:24:09.566
We have chosen it as a trademark
of 40 Days for Life in Croatia

00:24:09.766 --> 00:24:11.788
and our other pro-life associations.

00:24:27.788 --> 00:24:29.697
Every human life is precious.

00:24:29.897 --> 00:24:33.142
Every human life is unrepeatable
in the history of mankind.

00:24:33.342 --> 00:24:37.966
We are all unique and,
being aware of that,

00:24:38.166 --> 00:24:43.946
we want to make people
aware of their greatness.

00:24:44.146 --> 00:24:50.524
That we are all dignified
and beloved children of God.

00:24:50.724 --> 00:24:52.378
Precious children of God.

00:25:00.178 --> 00:25:03.152
Glory to the Father, and
to the Son, and to the Holy Spirit.

00:25:03.352 --> 00:25:07.594
As it was in the beginning,
and now, and ever shall be,

00:25:07.794 --> 00:25:09.866
world without end. Amen.

00:25:10.066 --> 00:25:14.376
I heard about 40 Days for Life
on Facebook actually.

00:25:14.576 --> 00:25:19.226
Even though all my life, as a believer,
I've felt that abortion was evil,

00:25:19.426 --> 00:25:23.506
I never had this experience
in my life, in my closest family.

00:25:23.706 --> 00:25:27.758
I considered 40 Days for Life
to be something positive,

00:25:27.958 --> 00:25:32.802
but I never had the experience
of its concrete work and activity

00:25:33.002 --> 00:25:36.478
until the moment this issue
came into my life.

00:25:36.678 --> 00:25:42.830
40 years ago I had
a negative experience with abortion.

00:25:43.030 --> 00:25:47.161
I already had two little girls,
age four and two,

00:25:47.361 --> 00:25:50.949
when I became pregnant
for the third time.

00:25:51.149 --> 00:25:57.369
Since I had no parents, there was
no one who could look after the baby,

00:25:57.569 --> 00:25:59.712
and I was working.

00:25:59.912 --> 00:26:05.248
There was no possiblity
for the baby to stay alive.

00:26:05.448 --> 00:26:11.081
Everything started happening for me
when abortion walked into my life

00:26:11.281 --> 00:26:15.167
through the situation with
my younger brother and his girlfriend.

00:26:15.367 --> 00:26:19.400
At that time, I didn't know
that he even had a girlfriend.

00:26:19.600 --> 00:26:23.896
One day I came to visit
my parents here,

00:26:24.096 --> 00:26:28.738
because I don't live in this city,
in Velika Gorica, any more.

00:26:28.938 --> 00:26:36.161
I came to visit my parents,
only to find my mother in tears.

00:26:36.361 --> 00:26:39.903
At the doctor's office,
I had a negative experience

00:26:40.103 --> 00:26:43.942
because of my naked body.

00:26:44.142 --> 00:26:50.627
A nurse came in and smiled
wondering about the situation.

00:26:50.827 --> 00:26:53.033
Tears started pouring out of nowhere.

00:26:53.233 --> 00:26:57.440
I wasn't conscious of that
state as I am now.

00:26:57.640 --> 00:27:04.154
And why I was crying so much.
I knew that it was murder,

00:27:04.354 --> 00:27:08.469
but it didn't affect me
as much as it did later.

00:27:08.669 --> 00:27:10.569
I asked what was happening,

00:27:10.769 --> 00:27:15.961
only to find out that
my brother had a girlfriend,

00:27:16.361 --> 00:27:21.712
that she was 17 and pregnant,

00:27:21.912 --> 00:27:23.867
and that they were
considering abortion.

00:27:24.067 --> 00:27:28.202
I went to confession and I cried.

00:27:28.402 --> 00:27:32.180
Everyone outside could have
heard what I had done.

00:27:32.380 --> 00:27:37.594
The priest was so understanding.
He didn't approve that,

00:27:37.794 --> 00:27:43.841
but he wanted to calm me down.

00:27:44.041 --> 00:27:47.779
He gave me absolution and
instructions. But I thought:

00:27:47.979 --> 00:27:50.627
"My dear Father,
this won't help me at all.

00:27:50.827 --> 00:27:54.812
I don't need absolution.
What I did, I can never forget."

00:27:55.012 --> 00:27:59.305
...and blessed is the fruit
of Thy womb Jesus.

00:27:59.505 --> 00:28:03.686
Holy Mary, Mother of God,
pray for us sinners,

00:28:03.886 --> 00:28:07.155
now and at the hour
of our death. Amen.

00:28:07.355 --> 00:28:13.147
I wait for the day, at my age.
I'm now in my golden age.

00:28:13.347 --> 00:28:17.948
I only wait for the day
to meet with my children,

00:28:18.148 --> 00:28:22.379
and when I see my little baby,
I will never let it go.

00:28:22.579 --> 00:28:26.360
I will take it in my arms and
never let it go. I will play with him.

00:28:26.560 --> 00:28:31.492
And worst of all, when the priest
asked me what I was using then.

00:28:31.692 --> 00:28:34.828
I admitted I had an intrauterine coil,
meaning there were even more babies.

00:28:35.028 --> 00:28:38.065
Which meant there occurred
a real genocide in my womb.

00:28:39.256 --> 00:28:42.416
I contacted 40 Days for Life
through Facebook.

00:28:42.616 --> 00:28:49.203
I got a response very quickly. I was
informed quite fast about everthing.

00:28:49.403 --> 00:28:51.877
40 Days for Life
is active in Velika Gorica.

00:28:52.077 --> 00:28:54.458
Together, we started
searching for a solution.

00:28:54.658 --> 00:28:57.239
People who I don't know
and who don't know me

00:28:57.439 --> 00:29:02.203
gave their 100% in prayer and fasting,

00:29:02.403 --> 00:29:05.923
and I felt the love and support

00:29:06.123 --> 00:29:09.186
which are actually
needed in a situation like this,

00:29:09.386 --> 00:29:11.607
for pregnant women,
fathers, and families.

00:29:11.807 --> 00:29:16.620
I am very sorry that
I did all this out of ignorance,

00:29:16.820 --> 00:29:22.054
and out of precaution that I wouldn't
be able to feed my children.

00:29:22.254 --> 00:29:26.513
And look what's happening today.
How many people come over,

00:29:26.713 --> 00:29:30.067
and there is always food
and there is always something left.

00:29:30.267 --> 00:29:36.005
And everyone is blessed.
But I have destroyed so many lives.

00:29:37.376 --> 00:29:44.060
I knew that I couldn't approach
my brother from a religious side,

00:29:44.260 --> 00:29:47.773
because this would result
in even greater resistance.

00:29:47.973 --> 00:29:50.881
I would then come across
an even greater wall.

00:29:51.081 --> 00:29:54.126
I tried talking to them about

00:29:54.326 --> 00:29:56.325
not so much about the sanctity of life,

00:29:56.525 --> 00:30:00.199
but about the fact that this
wasn't some dead-end situation.

00:30:00.399 --> 00:30:07.258
Before we went to the clinic,
we sat down for coffee at the mall,

00:30:07.458 --> 00:30:12.752
and the girl's phone was ringing
literally every 30 seconds.

00:30:12.952 --> 00:30:17.117
Her mom was checking where they were
and when they were going to do that.

00:30:18.392 --> 00:30:22.471
We weren't sure to the last minute
what was going to be the outcome.

00:30:22.671 --> 00:30:28.230
During that one-week drama,

00:30:28.430 --> 00:30:31.681
she showed great courage
and faith when she said,

00:30:31.881 --> 00:30:35.899
when she reached her final decision
and said that she didn't want to go,

00:30:36.099 --> 00:30:37.999
and that she had decided on life.

00:30:38.654 --> 00:30:41.015
All I can say is that,
at that moment,

00:30:42.058 --> 00:30:48.163
when that burden fell from my heart
and shoulders, that was indescribable.

00:30:48.363 --> 00:30:51.473
At that moment, I became aware that

00:30:51.673 --> 00:30:57.561
that wasn't something done by me or
40 Days for Life, but God's mercy.

00:30:58.355 --> 00:31:05.979
Where they, after 6 days,
23 hours and 58 minutes,

00:31:06.179 --> 00:31:10.757
of being absolutely sure about
abortion, simply chose life.

00:31:10.957 --> 00:31:16.094
It was God's mercy and an incredible
lesson for me to go forward.

00:31:19.937 --> 00:31:25.423
In different periods in history,
different battles were fought.

00:31:26.310 --> 00:31:31.032
In one period, people fought for one
thing, in another for something else.

00:31:31.232 --> 00:31:38.463
Our time is and will be great
because a person has stood up,

00:31:38.663 --> 00:31:41.369
a Christian who believes in God,

00:31:41.569 --> 00:31:46.260
to defend the life of an unborn baby

00:31:46.460 --> 00:31:51.680
that is threatened by every
persecution in this world.

00:32:51.015 --> 00:32:56.299
It is important to awaken
people who are believers,

00:32:56.499 --> 00:33:00.972
and who are often members
of some religious communities,

00:33:01.172 --> 00:33:03.278
and are involved as advocates for life,

00:33:03.478 --> 00:33:07.029
but who in certain moments,
when some difficulties occur,

00:33:07.229 --> 00:33:10.915
give up on their stance towards life
and reach for some measures

00:33:11.115 --> 00:33:12.851
which can later become a burden

00:33:13.051 --> 00:33:15.529
and which go against
the Lord's commandment.

00:33:15.729 --> 00:33:19.528
Therefore, it is important
to clearly point it out to people,

00:33:19.728 --> 00:33:25.534
to make it easier for them to take
a stand when they see people praying,

00:33:25.734 --> 00:33:31.012
when they see people who are publicly
advocating for the value of life.

00:33:31.212 --> 00:33:36.058
We know of three babies whose lives
have been saved in this campaign.

00:33:36.258 --> 00:33:41.277
Three new stories,
three new worlds.

00:33:41.477 --> 00:33:43.714
That is why these results are great.

00:33:43.914 --> 00:33:48.479
That is why tonight we have
a reason to really celebrate.

00:33:48.679 --> 00:33:51.046
We did not want to stop here.

00:33:51.246 --> 00:33:54.460
We wanted to raise awareness
in the local community

00:33:54.660 --> 00:33:58.381
about the problem of abortion
and the sanctity of human life.

00:33:58.581 --> 00:34:05.435
That is why we decided
to make this CD album

00:34:05.635 --> 00:34:09.038
with pro-life songs and prayers.

00:34:09.238 --> 00:34:15.379
We are certain that this album will
save at least one baby from abortion.

00:34:15.579 --> 00:34:17.274
You can be sure of that.

00:34:17.474 --> 00:34:19.896
We have the book ''40 Days for Life''.

00:34:27.477 --> 00:34:31.125
This baby that we can hear
was saved from abortion.

00:34:31.325 --> 00:34:34.556
There is also one more
mother and baby here.

00:34:39.290 --> 00:34:43.529
Benefactors’ evening, Zagreb, 2016

00:34:43.729 --> 00:34:48.032
I simply could not decide on
giving birth to my seventh baby

00:34:48.232 --> 00:34:52.902
until Miss Lidija invited me
to come to church on Monday.

00:34:53.102 --> 00:34:59.384
Just to come and be with them
and talk to them.

00:34:59.584 --> 00:35:02.294
They offered to help me
and give me everything I needed.

00:35:02.494 --> 00:35:08.040
They begged me not to abort this
baby, not to hurt myself and the baby.

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:10.708
I decided to come.

00:35:10.908 --> 00:35:14.528
The father who was there
talked to me about the situation.

00:35:14.728 --> 00:35:18.968
My 11-year-old daughter
who was with me told me:

00:35:19.168 --> 00:35:23.948
"Mom, don't abort my baby brother
or sister who is in your tummy."

00:35:24.148 --> 00:35:26.834
When I heard all the prayers
and everything,

00:35:27.034 --> 00:35:30.212
with God's help, I decided
not to go through with abortion.

00:35:30.412 --> 00:35:32.254
Thank you very much.

00:35:39.554 --> 00:35:43.727
I am especially glad and enthused by
how many people all over Croatia

00:35:43.927 --> 00:35:47.288
are getting involved in the initiative
and how many are organised,

00:35:47.488 --> 00:35:49.389
and how many join the prayer vigils.

00:35:49.589 --> 00:35:53.225
That's what makes us
one big pro-life family.

00:35:53.425 --> 00:35:55.277
And the Word became Flesh.

00:35:55.477 --> 00:36:00.392
God became present
in our lives, for our world.

00:36:00.592 --> 00:36:06.133
He became present for us, personally.
For each and every one of us.

00:36:06.333 --> 00:36:10.670
He became God who is
present in our sufferings,

00:36:10.870 --> 00:36:14.604
in our toils, our crises,
and our struggles.

00:36:14.804 --> 00:36:18.108
He also wants to be
present in victories,

00:36:18.308 --> 00:36:22.235
in recoveries, in healings,
and in deliverances.

00:36:22.435 --> 00:36:27.708
He wants to be present every day
and in every moment of our lives.

00:36:27.908 --> 00:36:29.767
That's why it is important to realise

00:36:29.967 --> 00:36:34.017
that we are also invited
to this God's presence

00:36:34.217 --> 00:36:38.230
in places where one suffers,
where one stumbles out of weariness,

00:36:38.430 --> 00:36:44.475
where one is sick and carries a cross,
and where one is in need of mercy.

00:36:44.675 --> 00:36:48.463
That is why our fight for life
is one big presence.

00:37:38.930 --> 00:37:44.065
40 Days for Life is that something
which radically changes your life.

00:37:44.265 --> 00:37:50.038
When we started, I had no idea
that I would meet so many mothers,

00:37:50.238 --> 00:37:54.463
so many children,
whose lives would change my life.

00:37:54.663 --> 00:37:58.515
The relationship with our mothers,
when I meet a mother

00:37:58.715 --> 00:38:01.229
or when I meet a baby
that was saved from abortion,

00:38:01.429 --> 00:38:05.295
no other feeling can replace
that joy and happiness.

00:38:05.495 --> 00:38:07.609
When you hold this baby in your arms,

00:38:07.809 --> 00:38:14.305
no matter the uncertainty in its life,
the life of its mother or our own,

00:38:14.505 --> 00:38:20.110
that child and that life is worth
fighting for in this initiative.

00:38:20.310 --> 00:38:25.117
And every soul of a mother or a baby
is what motivates us to go forward

00:38:25.317 --> 00:38:27.580
and what motivates me personally

00:38:27.780 --> 00:38:30.599
to get up in the morning
and keep on fighting for life.

00:39:27.358 --> 00:39:29.964
"No one can do it for me,

00:39:30.164 --> 00:39:35.574
to carry my cross,
to fulfil your plan.

00:39:35.774 --> 00:39:38.195
No one can do it for me,

00:39:38.395 --> 00:39:43.765
to overcome my fears,
to endure my battles.

00:39:43.965 --> 00:39:47.203
Because You call me by my name.

00:39:47.403 --> 00:39:52.268
I am neither a letter nor a number,
but engraved in the palm of Your hand.

00:39:52.468 --> 00:39:55.722
You call me by my name.

00:39:55.922 --> 00:40:03.411
I am neither a letter nor a number,
but the one You died for.

00:40:03.611 --> 00:40:07.534
And this is my life.
My fight and my pain.

00:40:07.734 --> 00:40:12.087
My joy and salvation,
and cross, and blessing.

00:40:12.287 --> 00:40:15.834
This is my life.
My fight and pain.

00:40:16.034 --> 00:40:24.145
My joy and salvation, and cross,
and a blessing from Heaven.

00:40:26.145 --> 00:40:28.894
No one can do it for you,

00:40:29.394 --> 00:40:34.450
to carry your cross,
to fulfil His plan.

00:40:34.650 --> 00:40:37.368
No one can do it for you,

00:40:37.568 --> 00:40:42.724
to walk your paths, to consecrate
oneself through your suffering.

00:40:42.924 --> 00:40:46.196
Because He calls you by your name.

00:40:46.396 --> 00:40:51.153
You are neither a letter nor a number,
He engraved you in the palm of His hand.

00:40:51.353 --> 00:40:54.676
God calls you by your name.

00:40:54.876 --> 00:41:02.842
You are neither a letter nor a number,
but the one He died for.

00:41:03.042 --> 00:41:06.455
And this is your life.
Your fight and pain.

00:41:06.655 --> 00:41:11.077
Your joy and salvation,
and cross, and blessing.

00:41:11.277 --> 00:41:14.809
This is your life.
Your fight and pain.

00:41:15.009 --> 00:41:22.742
Your joy and salvation, and cross,
and a blessing from Heaven.

00:41:22.942 --> 00:41:27.499
Believe that there is love,
bigger than any fear,

00:41:27.699 --> 00:41:31.233
bigger than any pain.

00:41:31.433 --> 00:41:36.241
Believe that there is a hand
which embraces you

00:41:36.441 --> 00:41:40.083
every time somebody leaves you.

00:41:40.383 --> 00:41:44.208
This is my life. My fight and pain.

00:41:44.408 --> 00:41:48.888
My joy and salvation,
and cross, and blessing.

00:41:49.088 --> 00:41:52.756
This is my life.
My fight and pain.

00:41:52.956 --> 00:41:57.445
My joy and salvation,
and cross, and blessing…"

00:41:57.645 --> 00:42:00.556
From 2004 to 2018, more than
750,000 people in 50 countries.

00:42:00.756 --> 00:42:02.933
have actively participated
in 40 Days for Life.

00:42:03.133 --> 00:42:06.520
More than 14,700 babies have been saved
and 96 abortion clinics closed.

00:42:06.720 --> 00:42:08.845
More than 180 abortion
workers quit their job.

00:42:09.045 --> 00:42:11.295
40 Days for Life
has impacted millions of people.

00:42:11.495 --> 00:42:14.645
In Croatia, more than 10,000 people
have participated in 29 cities.

00:42:14.845 --> 00:42:18.745
In some hospitals, the number of abortions
has dropped for more than 50 per cent,

00:42:18.945 --> 00:42:21.145
and we know of 57 babies
that have been saved.

00:42:21.345 --> 00:42:24.945
The abortion problem has become one of
the most common subjects in society.

